{"type":"message","id":"6fa169e4","parentId":"8e726fb1","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:39:33.631Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session in the last 5 minutes is the cron job itself. There's no actual user conversation happening. So I should proceed with the self-learning task.\n\nLet me search for information about:\n1. Enterprise digital transformation\n2. Smart security/smart安防\n3. Network system integration\n4. IT operations and maintenance services\n\nI'll use the web search skill to find relevant industry news.","thinkingSignature":"2804718a1024fbfe4558aaa44c6b52c4a0e79b83ebe22feadf87b8e0d1d1c22d"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有 cron 任务自身在运行，没有用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_27cxphm2iarv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":923,"output":143,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45047,"cost":{"input":0.0002769,"output":0.0001716,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00176793}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775097569174}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9d2f75b","parentId":"6fa169e4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:39:33.641Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_27cxphm2iarv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775097573638}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e6c7445","parentId":"b9d2f75b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:39:39.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to search for information about the relevant industries. Let me search for:\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业趋势\n4. IT运维服务行业趋势\n\nI'll do these searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"78e48d31b1d9fc0967ef5ef8f94358ec9a0f2f68657fde1a65050d189d04c14e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c3es7lqlnsxy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c3es7lqlnsxy_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c3es7lqlnsxy_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1581,"output":237,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45799,"cost":{"input":0.0004743,"output":0.0002844,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00207813}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775097573641}}
